title: NYC Restrictive and Environmental Declaration Locations (Zoning)
name: NYC Restrictive and Environmental Declaration Locations (Zoning)
description: Point features representing the approximate within-tax-block locations for tax lots subject to environmental or restrictive declarations. These locations are equivalent to the "E" and "D" markers formerly shown on the DCP zoning map. Declaration designations are indicated in the DECNO attribute.
